# University Brand Logos

Drop institution logos in this folder using the slug as the filename:

  usm.png     → Universiti Sains Malaysia
  um.png      → Universiti Malaya
  utm.png     → Universiti Teknologi Malaysia
  ukm.png     → Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia
  upm.png     → Universiti Putra Malaysia
  uitm.png    → Universiti Teknologi MARA
  iium.png    → International Islamic University Malaysia
  uthm.png    → Universiti Tun Hussein Onn
  unimap.png  → Universiti Malaysia Perlis
  taylors.png → Taylor's University
  sunway.png  → Sunway University
  monash.png  → Monash University Malaysia
  inti.png    → INTI International University
  help.png    → HELP University
  ucsi.png    → UCSI University
  mmu.png     → Multimedia University
  apu.png     → Asia Pacific University
  psp.png     → Politeknik Seberang Perai
  puo.png     → Politeknik Ungku Omar
  kptm.png    → Kolej Poli-Tech MARA
  gmi.png     → German-Malaysian Institute
  ...

Full list of detectable institutions lives in:
  app/Models/CultureEvent.php  →  const UNIVERSITY_BRANDS

The matcher looks for ANY alias substring inside the lowercased
`university` field, so admins can type "Universiti Sains Malaysia"
or just "USM" — both resolve to usm.png.

Accepted extensions (checked in order): svg → png → webp → jpg → jpeg.

Display rules on the public intern card:
  1. If a logo file exists here          → render as <img>
  2. Else if abbreviation is known       → render a styled badge
                                           (gold-on-navy pill, e.g. "USM")
  3. Else                                 → fall back to the institution_type
                                           Font Awesome icon

So the feature works immediately with the styled abbreviation badge —
dropping logo files just upgrades each one to real brand artwork.
